scenario.title: Add MCO Admin user in system option
scenario.step: Given user navigated to landing page
When new user logs to Internal User portal with username - internal.user.dyp+cd@gmail.com and password - Internaluser1!
When click on 'Agree' button in the Portal page
Then statistics should be displayed on dashboard page
When navigate to 'System Options' page from user pop-up
Then click on 'Users' links in system options
When Click on Add User button from User page
Then Verifying Add new user pop-up is opened
When fill User firstname field with value 'MCO'
When fill User lastname field with value 'ADMIN'
When select role 'MCO Admin' from the user list
